nntpspider (0.1) unstable; urgency=high

  * a very big step forward. Now it's in real alpha state.
  * using commandline switches
  * configurable filenames for serverlist, resultlist and grouplist
  * differentiate three levels of verbosity: normal/verbose/debug mode
  * improved readability of the debug output
  * fixed many bugs in the connection error handling
  * Added a simple Makefile
  * using correct mail adress

